Source: secubox-newsbin
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: secubox-newsbin
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), python3-uvicorn
Recommends: docker.io | podman
Description: Usenet downloader management for SecuBox
 SecuBox module for managing SABnzbd Usenet downloader via Docker.
 Provides NZB download management, queue control, Usenet server
 configuration, categories, and post-processing support.
 .
 Features:
  - SABnzbd container management (Docker/Podman)
  - NZB file/URL handling
  - Download queue with pause/resume
  - Usenet server configuration
  - Category organization
  - Download history and statistics
 .
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/newsbin/ via Unix socket.
